635
00:49:18,392 --> 00:49:20,983
<font face="Serif" size="18">mantener el entusiasmo.</font>

636
00:49:41,544 --> 00:49:43,550
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rita, tienes un mensaje.</font>

637
00:49:48,314 --> 00:49:49,567
<font face="Serif" size="18">Es Coral.</font>

638
00:49:49,567 --> 00:49:50,946
<font face="Serif" size="18">Otra vez lo mismo.</font>

639
00:49:50,946 --> 00:49:53,370
<font face="Serif" size="18">Solo hemos estudiado
